title: DAZ3D - Shackled! Genesis 3
description:
---Previously uploaded to KAT by ArgosDaz---

Shackled! for Genesis 3 is a set of props, smartprops and a conformer for Genesis 3 in Daz Studio with Iray. It includes several props to help you restrain up male and female characters with chains, including single and double shackles, a ball and chain, a torso chain setup, and many sizes and lengths of individual rigged chain props.

As a bonus, this set also includes a dungeon-style wall and some presets for creating wall and floor setups with it!
